description: A dashboard for visualizing results from the k6.io load testing tool, using the InfluxDB exporter.Based on https://grafana.com/dashboards/4411

targets.query: SELECT max("value") FROM "http_req_duration" WHERE ("name" =~ /^$URL$/ AND "group" =~ /^$Group$/ AND "scenario" =~ /^$Scenarios$/) AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time($__interval) fill(null)
SELECT percentile("value", 95) FROM "http_req_duration" WHERE ("name" =~ /^$URL$/ AND "group" = 'select tag value') AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time(10s)

SELECT count("value"), min("value"), median("value"), max("value"), mean("value"), percentile("value", 95) FROM /^$Measurement$/ WHERE ("scenario" =~ /^$Scenarios$/ AND "group" =~ /^$Group$/ AND "name" =~ /^$URL$/) AND $timeFilter GROUP BY "group", "name"

title: Rio Performance
